content: Both `arch-primitive` (https://tinyurl.com/qlj5e4t) and `arch-primitive-ion` (https://tinyurl.com/tlsvob6) are available at Docker Hub. You should try something that is faster than caching proxy.

Working on the new `Noozxoide EIZO-NNXT Series` after leaving the workplace. This firmware takes digital audio signals with added special effects to makes the listening content realistic, immersive and stunning sound.

The latest firmware enables `sonar.ai` to self-labeling raw data. A set of neural-network that helps with this cool feature, saving me plenty of time for data labeling manually. It's a new breakthrough in my lab.
